-----------------------------------------------------------------------------

Node.js and NPM/Yarn/PNPM Specific Ignore List

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------

Dependencies

Standard dependency directory (MUST be ignored)

/node_modules

Yarn PnP files (for modern dependency resolution)

.pnp.*
.yarn/cache
.yarn/unplugged
.yarn/build-state.yml
.yarn/install-state.yml

Compiled output and build artifacts

These are generated files, not source code

/dist
/build
/out
/es
/public/dist

Logs and Debugging

NPM debug log files

npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
pnpm-debug.log*

General runtime logs

*.log
/log
/logs

Testing and Coverage

/coverage
*.func.js
*.prof

Environment variables and sensitive data

Local and sensitive environment configuration files

These should never be committed as they contain credentials or local settings

.env
.env.local
.env.*.local

Database/Temp files (e.g., SQLite files, temp caches)

*.sqlite
*.sqlite3
/tmp
/temp
/cache

IDE and OS generated files

VS Code

.vscode/

IntelliJ / WebStorm

.idea/

macOS system files

.DS_Store

Windows system files

Thumbs.db

Other common development tools

*.swp